<section>
<p id="intro">Angband is a free, single-player dungeon exploration game.  You take the role of an adventurer: seeking riches, fighting monsters, and preparing for a final battle with Morgoth, the Lord of Darkness.</p>
</section>

<section class="slots">
<div class="slot">
<img src="/img/shot1.png" width="175" height="175">
<p class="caption">You (the <tt>@</tt>) begin in the small trading town above Angband, ready to descend into its depths (using the down staircase, '<tt>></tt>').
</div>

<div class="slot">
<img src="/img/shot2.png" width="175" height="175">
<p class="caption">You explore randomly-generated caverns, and find treasure: <tt>=</tt> is a ring, <tt>?</tt> is a scroll.
</div>

<div class="slot">
<img src="/img/shot3.png" width="180" height="175">
<p class="caption">You fight monsters.  <tt>o</tt> is an orc, <tt>p</tt> a human, and <tt>r</tt> a rat.  If you die in battle, you have to start the game again!
</div>

<div class="slot">
<img src="/img/shot4.png" width="180" height="175">
<p class="caption">Graphics are also available if ASCII isn't your style.
</div>
</section>

